                <span class="field-content"><a href="/periods/modern/new-palace-westminster"><h3 class="title">The New Palace of Westminster</h3></a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-phpcode">
                <span class="field-content">The fire of 1834, which destroyed much but not all of the old palace of Westminster,  provided an opportunity to put into place some of the long existing  hopes and plans for a purpose-built Parliament. After a controversial  competition, and amid seemingly interminable wrangling, the project was ...</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-view-node">
